      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "HIGH CUBE (1) has a strong record this track and trip with 12 wins and 11 placings from 31 starts. Comes off a (23.07) win last time, scoring by half a length in a Grade 4/5 over 400m at this track. Looks a leading chance on best. RITZA BENJI (3) finds it hard to win but looks close to breaking through. Has hit the frame the last two runs, the latest when second (29.92) at this track. Solid record at the distance winning five races. The form from his last run stacks up well. Deserves a win and gets his chance. JAMARRA (8) produced a handy 29.88 when placed over 512m at this track last start in a Grade 5. Harder here but will be in this for a long way. WAY COOL (4) won last start in the fastest time on the card. Must be respected.",
